        <activityName xml:lang="en">market for aircraft, agricultural</activityName>
        <includedActivitiesStart xml:lang="en">This activity starts at the gate of the activities that produce 'aircraft, agricultural', within the geography of Global.</includedActivitiesStart>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">This activity ends with the supply of 'aircraft, agricultural', to the consumers of this product. Transport or losses are considered irrelevant for this product.</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This is a market activity. Each market represents the consumption mix of a product in a given geography, connecting suppliers with consumers of the same product in the same geographical area. Markets group the producers and also the imports of the product (if relevant) within the same geographical area. They also account for transport to the consumer and for the losses during that process, when relevant. </text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="1">This is the market for 'aircraft, agricultural' in the Global geography.</text>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="2">No transport is considered in this market. Potential initial transfer of the airplane from the production site is neglected.</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
      <classification classificationId="a552e7c0-f0b1-4da2-a5b4-965cd7a61450">
        <classificationSystem xml:lang="en">ISIC rev.4 ecoinvent</classificationSystem>
